description: You could say I've been waiting for this moment since 2013. I thought I got too over-excited for Skerryvore, but wow this was a different level of meme. It's a shame really, I'm sure it's not all meme but like, we all know I was waiting for that one song to be reminded of Chad Michael Murray bouncing the Chadsketball along the bridge. Nah Mr. DeGraw was amazing though. I enjoy far more of his pieces than my meme'ing may indicate.
